Project creation specification
=====================
     
Project creation BDD test
----------------

Мы создадим новый проект, назначим ему менеджера.
Затем проверим, что проект создан корректно. Будем использовать библиотеку Masqurade.

* Open application in the browser
* Log in as user with "dev1" username and "dev1" password
* Open the project browser
* Open the project editor
* Fill from fields with following values: name is "BDD testing", manager is "admin"
* Save new project
* Make sure the new project with "BDD testing" name is added to project table